import { Divider } from "@material-ui/core"

const MainForm = ({text, setText, day , setDay}) => {
    return (
        <>
            <Divider />
                <form>
                    <label>
                        Name:
                        <input type="text" name="name" />
                    </label>
                    <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
                </form>
            <Divider />
        </>
    )
}

export default MainForm
